      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAFFERTY BLUES (2) jumped cleanly from the low draw last start to lead all the way (19.80) at this track in a Invitation over 342m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and can measure up. DARK MOONSHINE (1) is suited by the inside draw. Last start finished 2nd on April 13 over 342m at this track behind Son Of Maple beaten 4.5 lengths (19.87) in a OPEN. Looks one of the chances. JASON ROSE (4) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 2.25 lengths away in second (19.86) at this track in a Grade 5 over 342m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from eight attempts. Can measure up. ALL THE SASS (8) is a last start winner in very good time. Right in the mix.",
